===解聚技術===
以化學及/或酵素將肝素解聚的技術，對於肝素或硫酸肝素的結構與功能的研究有重大的貢獻。

====酵素解聚====
分解肝素與硫酸肝素的酵素通常來自於土壤中的[[解肝磷脂土地桿菌|解肝磷脂土地桿菌]]<ref>{{cite journal | author= Shaya D | title = Crystal structure of heparinase II from Pedobacter heparinus and its complex with a disaccharide product | journal= J. Biol. Chem. | year=2006 | volume=281 | issue=22 | pages=15525–15535 | pmid = 16565082 | doi = 10.1074/jbc.M512055200|name-list-format=vanc | author2 =  Tocilj A. |display-authors=etal}}</ref>。解肝磷脂土地桿菌以肝素或硫酸肝素作為它的唯一碳源，為了分解肝素與硫酸肝素，解肝磷脂土地桿菌產生[[裂合酶|裂解酶]]，葡糖苷酸酶，磺基酯酶和磺酰胺酶<ref>{{cite journal | author= Galliher PM | title = Heparinase production by Flavobacterium heparinum | url= https://archive.org/details/sim_applied-and-environmental-microbiology_1981-02_41_2/page/n35 | journal= Appl. Environ. Microbiol. | year=1981 | volume=41 | issue=2 | pages=360–365 | pmid = 7235692 | pmc= 243699|name-list-format=vanc | author2 =  Cooney CL. |display-authors=etal}}</ref> ，最常使用的是裂解酶。解肝磷脂土地桿菌共產生三種裂解酶：肝素酶 I （{{EC number|4.2.2.7}}）、肝素酶 II （沒有[[EC編號|EC編號]]）、肝素酶 III （{{EC number|4.2.2.8}}），這三個酵素的專一性詳見下表： <ref>{{cite journal | author= Linhardt RJ | title = Examination of the substrate specificity of heparin and heparan sulfate lyases | journal= Biochemistry | year=1990 | volume=29 | issue=10 | pages=2611–2617 | pmid = 2334685 | doi = 10.1021/bi00462a026|name-list-format=vanc | author2 =  Turnbull JE. |display-authors=etal}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=Desai UR |author2=Wang HM. |author3=Linhardt RJ. | title = Specificity studies on the heparin lyases from Flavobacterium heparinum | journal= Biochemistry | year=1993 | volume=32 | issue=32 | pages=8140–8145 | pmid = 8347612 | doi = 10.1021/bi00083a012}}</ref>

