===肝素的產製===
製藥級的肝素是從[[屠宰|屠宰]]動物的[[黏膜|黏膜]]（如[[家豬|豬]]腸或[[牛|牛]]肺）純化而來<ref>{{cite journal | author = Linhardt RJ, Gunay NS. | title = Production and Chemical Processing of Low Molecular Weight Heparins | journal = Sem. Thromb. Hem. | year=1999 | volume=3 | pages=5–16 | pmid = 10549711 | last2 = Gunay }}</ref>。全合成肝素的技術正持續地研發<ref>{{cite web|last=Bhattacharya|first=Ananyo|title=Flask synthesis promises untainted heparin|url=http://www.rsc.org/chemistryworld/News/2008/August/19080803.asp|work=Chemistry World|publisher=Royal Society of Chemistry|accessdate=6 February 2011|date=August 2008|archive-date=2012-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021055549/http://www.rsc.org/chemistryworld/News/2008/August/19080803.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以化學酶法工藝從雙糖合成低分子量肝素的方法已在2011年被研發出來<ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1126/science.1207478| pmid = 22034431| title = Chemoenzymatic Synthesis of Homogeneous Ultralow Molecular Weight Heparins| journal = Science| volume = 334| issue = 6055| pages = 498–501| year = 2011| last1 = Xu | first1 = Y.| last2 = Masuko | first2 = S.| last3 = Takieddin | first3 = M.| last4 = Xu | first4 = H.| last5 = Liu | first5 = R.| last6 = Jing | first6 = J.| last7 = Mousa | first7 = S. A.| last8 = Linhardt | first8 = R. J.| last9 = Liu | first9 = J.
| pmc = 3425363}}</ref>。

===研究===
